# UI Consistency Rules

- Similar problems should use the same interaction pattern.
- Forms, tables, filters, dialogs, toasts, and navigation must follow shared patterns.
- Respect hierarchy: page > section > group > component > element.
- Default to system variants before introducing custom styling.
- Audit all new screens for state coverage and component reuse.
